<ol>
<li>Rotations to degrees =&gt; <code>* 360</code></li>
<li>Gearbox input to gearbox output =&gt; <code>stage1 ratio * stage2 ratio * .... * stageN ratio</code> where “ratio” is <code>output/input</code> so 100:1 == 1/100</li>
<li>Rotations to inches =&gt; <code>* circumference</code></li>
